---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Headshot Photographers — Client Testimonials That Fill Your Studio | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic client testimonials for your headshot photography business. Build trust and book more sessions. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Headshot Photographers</p>
        <h1>Professionals trust other professionals — show them who has trusted you</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Corporate clients and actors choosing a headshot photographer want to see real results AND real testimonials. SocialProof makes it easy to collect both.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why headshot photographers struggle to convert website traffic</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Portfolio alone isn't enough</h3>
            <p>Your portfolio is stunning. But a potential client can't tell from your photos alone if the experience was good, if you were professional, if the turnaround was fast. Testimonials fill those gaps.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 LinkedIn recommendations aren't on your website</h3>
            <p>Satisfied clients write you glowing LinkedIn recommendations. Beautiful — but no one reads LinkedIn profiles when they're booking a photographer. Get those words on your site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 Corporate clients need to feel safe booking</h3>
            <p>When a marketing manager books headshots for 20 employees, they need confidence. A testimonial from a similar company is the closer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>Share your unique form link via text, email, or QR code. Send the link right after delivering the final photos — clients are excited and the experience is fresh.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Approve the keepers. Hide the rest.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag. Paste it anywhere — your homepage, booking page, bio link. Add it to your services page, your booking page, or right next to your portfolio galleries.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Headshot Photographers</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Collect written testimonials with optional star ratings. Shows visitors exactly what to expect.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Customer photos</h3>
            <p>Let clients add a photo or headshot. Real faces build real trust.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Matches your brand</h3>
            <p>Customize colors, fonts, and layout so the widget looks native on your site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Works on any device</h3>
            <p>Your customers fill the form on their phone. The widget looks great on mobile too.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 You own the data</h3>
            <p>Testimonials live in your account, not on a third-party platform. No lock-in.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
